      "box": [
        555,
        160,
        919,
        180
      ],
      "score": 0.9952223896980286
    },
    {
      "text": "20. En verdad, en verdad os digo, que vosotros llorareis,",
      "box": [
        86,
        174,
        445,
        195
      ],
      "score": 0.9993667602539062
    },
    {
